{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about","content_id":"5f5ad137-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"UK Visas and Immigration (UKVI) is responsible for making millions of decisions every year about who has the right to visit or stay in the country, with a firm emphasis on national security and a culture of customer satisfaction for people who come here legally. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/customer-service-commitments-uk-visas-and-immigration\">Our customer charter</a> sets out the service UK Visas and Immigration aims to provide its customers and what it expects from them.</p>\n\n<p>We have a workforce of 7,500 people based in locations around the UK and overseas. Our staff work on high volume services and more specialist casework.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-responsibilities\">Our responsibilities</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>to run the UK’s visa service, managing around 3 million applications a year from overseas nationals who wish to come to the UK to visit, study or work</li>\n  <li>to consider applications for British citizenship from overseas nationals who wish to settle here permanently</li>\n  <li>to run the UK’s asylum service offering protection to those eligible under the 1951 Geneva Convention</li>\n  <li>\n    <p>to decide applications from employers and educational establishments who want to join the register of sponsors</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>to manage appeals from unsuccessful applicants</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-priorities\">Our priorities</h2>\n\n<p>We contribute to achieving the Home Office’s priorities of securing our borders and reducing immigration, cutting crime and protecting our citizens from terrorism.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2014-04-23T08:24:00Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["5f5609b3-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef"],"name":"Access our information"},{"contents":["4ba28ca6-9bea-4afe-9fee-1eae95b1671c"],"name":"Jobs and contracts"}],"headers":[{"id":"who-we-are","level":2,"text":"Who we are"},{"id":"our-responsibilities","level":2,"text":"Our responsibilities"},{"id":"our-priorities","level":2,"text":"Our priorities"}],"organisation":"04148522-b0c1-4137-b687-5f3c3bdd561a","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2014-04-23T10:24:00+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about","content_id":"5f5ad137-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-04-23T08:24:00Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about","withdrawn":false}],"corporate_information_pages":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about/recruitment","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about/recruitment","base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about/recruitment","content_id":"4ba28ca6-9bea-4afe-9fee-1eae95b1671c","document_type":"recruitment","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-09-28T08:23:15Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Working for UKVI","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about/recruitment","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about/complaints-procedure","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/uk-visas-and-immigration/about/complaints-procedure","base_path":"/government/organisat